# @gravity-ui/eslint-config/prettier

Optional sub-config for projects using Prettier. Import alongside the base config to disable ESLint rules that conflict with Prettier formatting.

## Usage

```js
import baseConfig from '@gravity-ui/eslint-config';
import prettierConfig from '@gravity-ui/eslint-config/prettier';

export default [
  ...baseConfig,
  ...prettierConfig,
  {
    // ...other config
  },
];
```

