# @gravity-ui/eslint-config/import-order

Optional sub-config that enforces a convention in module import order. Import alongside the base config to enable import ordering rules.

## Usage

```js
import baseConfig from '@gravity-ui/eslint-config';
import importOrderConfig from '@gravity-ui/eslint-config/import-order';

export default [
  ...baseConfig,
  ...importOrderConfig,
  {
    // ...other config
  },
];
```
